Problem description :

Given a string, determine if it is a palindrome, considering only alphanumeric characters and ignoring cases.

For example,
"A man, a plan, a canal: Panama" is a palindrome.
"race a car" is not a palindrome.


Solution:
Use two pointer to direct the head and tail to check whether the two character is same. If not, the string is not palindrome, if it is,
check the next two character.

tips:
Only considering the numeric and character!
